<% content_for :header do %>
<h1 class="animated fadeInDown delay">
  The Community Distribution of Kubernetes that powers <a href="https://www.openshift.com" class="headerlink" target="_blank" style="font-weight: 400;">Red Hat OpenShift</a>.
