        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-6">
          <h2>Get Started</h2>
          <p>All contributions are welcome! OKD uses the Apache 2 license and does not require any contributor agreement to submit patches.
              Please open issues for any bugs or problems you encounter, ask questions in the <b>#openshift-dev</b> on Kubernetes Slack Channel,
              or get involved in the OKD-WG by joining the OKD-WG google group.
              <br>
              <ul>              
                <li>
                  Get started with the
                  <a href="https://github.com/openshift/okd/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md">Contributors Guide</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                  Fork
                  <a href="https://github.com/openshift/origin">the repository</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                  Read the
                  <a href="https://docs.okd.io/latest/welcome/index.html">documentation</a>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <br><a href="https://github.com/openshift/okd/blob/master/LICENSE">Apache 2 license</a>
              <br><a href="https://github.com/openshift/okd/issues">Open issues</a>
              <br><a href="https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/okd-wg">OKD-WG google group</a>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-6">
          <h2>Connect to the community</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Join the
              <a href="https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/okd-wg">OKD Working Group</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              Attend an upcoming
              <a href="https://github.com/openshift/community/projects/1">OKD Working Group Meeting</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
